data.text:
Recruit and return: Ohio State Buckeyes

To return to the NCAA tournament, a team needs contributions from both returning players and incoming recruits. Here's a look at Ohio State and its chances of dancing again in 2016.

about 3432 days ago | John Stovall | NCB On The Trail

National Prep Showcase Day 1 recap

NEW HAVEN, Conn. -- If you look at the National Prep Showcase with a wide lens, you'll notice that the event serves two purposes. The high-end talent has a major platform in which to state their case and solidify their standing amongst their peers.

about 4285 days ago | Dave Telep

Donte Clark heads Hokies class

First-year Virginia Tech head coach James Johnson announced his 2013 signing class on Thursday. Leading the way is ESPN 100 SF Donte Clark (Charlotte, N.C./Hargrave Military).

about 4288 days ago | NCB On The Trail

Virginia Tech adds Texas SG

Shooting guard Ben Emelogu (Grand Prairie, Texas/South Grand Prairie) gave a verbal commitment to Virginia Tech on Saturday, ESPN.com has confirmed. Emelogu is the fourth recruit in 2013 for the Hokies and the second to commit in the last week.

about 4321 days ago | RecruitingNation | NCB On The Trail

C Maurice Kirby pledges to Hokies

Big man Maurice Kirby (San Tan Valley, Ariz./Basha) gave a verbal commitment to Virginia Tech on Thursday, according toazcentral.com. The 6-foot-8 Kirby originally committed to Arizona State as a sophomore in 2010.

about 4323 days ago | RecruitingNation | NCB On The Trail

Hokies keep Hargrave pipeline going

Hargrave Military Academy (Chatham, Va.) has been a feeder program for the Virginia Tech Hokies. Coach James Johnson's team has three former Hargrave players on the roster this year, and next season that number will rise to four.

about 4341 days ago | Dave Telep

Virginia Tech lands ESPN 100 SF

ESPN 100 small forward Donte Clark (Charlotte, N.C./Hargrave Military) verbally committed to Virginia Tech on Sunday following his official visit to Blacksburg, ESPN.com has confirmed.

about 4341 days ago | RecruitingNation | NCB On The Trail
